<section class="panel">
  <div class="card-grid card-grid-three">
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">explore</span>
      <h2>Go-to-Definition</h2>
      <p>Jump to symbol definitions across your entire solution — including into decompiled NuGet packages and BCL source.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">psychology</span>
      <h2>Completions &amp; Hover Docs</h2>
      <p>Roslyn-powered IntelliSense with full XML doc comments, signature help, and overload resolution.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">build</span>
      <h2>Code Actions &amp; Refactoring</h2>
      <p>Rename symbol, extract method, generate constructor, fix-all diagnostics — all via standard LSP code actions.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">format_paint</span>
      <h2>Formatting</h2>
      <p>C# formatting via Roslyn. F# formatting via Fantomas. EditorConfig respected. Works in every editor.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">error</span>
      <h2>Real-time Diagnostics</h2>
      <p>Roslyn compiler errors and warnings as you type. No separate build step required to see errors inline.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">view_in_ar</span>
      <h2>NuGet Integration</h2>
      <p>Search, install, and update NuGet packages without leaving your editor or running CLI commands.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

