  <div class="copy-block">
    <h2>Ditch Visual Studio. Keep Your Editor.</h2>
    <p>Visual Studio is Windows-only and forces you into a heavyweight IDE. SharpLsp brings the same Roslyn language intelligence to VS Code, Zed, and more — on Windows, macOS, and Linux. No IDE required.</p>
  </div>
</section>

